  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides options for configuring an XPS document created by <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.SKDocument" />.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKDocumentXpsOptions` configures the XPS document created by
<xref:SkiaSharp.SKDocument.CreateXps*>. Set the `DPI` property to control the
rasterization resolution and `AllowNoPngs` to control whether the encoder is
allowed to omit PNG fallbacks for vector content.

This struct is a value type and does not require disposal.

## Examples

```csharp
var options = new SKDocumentXpsOptions
{
    DPI = 150.0f,
    AllowNoPngs = false,
};

using var stream = new SKFileWStream("output.xps");
using var document = SKDocument.CreateXps(stream, options.DPI);
var canvas = document.BeginPage(595, 842);
// draw content...
document.EndPage();
document.Close();
```
]]></format></remarks>
